  | last = Randall
  | first = Lisa
  | title = Knocking on Heaven's Door: How Physics and Scientific Thinking Illuminate the Universe and the Modern World
  | publisher = HarperCollins
  | year = 2011
  | pages =pp. 219
  | isbn = 9780062096890
}}</ref>很多[[大學|大學]]與國家型實驗室也在之後幾年陸續加入。至今，仍有許多研究機構與物理學者新參與此計畫。探測器組件是由各個研究機構分別研發製造，於2003年，這些組件開始被運送至CERN的ATLAS實驗所在地進行組裝。

2008年ATLAS實驗設施安裝完畢。<ref>{{cite web | url =http://www.atlas.ch/news/2008/jigsaw-puzzle.html | title =ATLAS completes world's largest jigsaw puzzle | last =Perkins | first =Ceri | date =Feb 2008 | publisher =Atlas.ch | deadurl =yes | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160305092935/http://www.atlas.ch/news/2008/jigsaw-puzzle.html | archivedate =2016-03-05 }}</ref>同年9月10日，ATLAS實驗第一次探測到粒子束事件。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.atlas.ch/news/2008/first-beam-and-event.html |title=First beam and first events in ATLAS |publisher=Atlas.ch |accessdate=2008-09-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706221650/http://www.atlas.ch/news/2008/first-beam-and-event.html |archivedate=2011-07-06 }}</ref>9天後，在暖機過程時，發生[[超導磁鐵|磁體失超]]事件，<ref group="註">磁體失超指的是，由於[[超導磁鐵|超導磁鐵]]的局部過熱，失去超導性質。假若發生磁體失超，[[電阻|電阻]]可能會重新出現，因此引起[[焦耳加熱|焦耳加熱]]（Joule heating），熱能快速蔓延至整個磁鐵，使得磁鐵周圍的冷卻劑開始沸騰。</ref>使得收集數據的工作延遲了1年多。修理耗費了幾個月時間，電路缺陷探測系統與快速失超控制系統的功能也被大幅度提升。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://press.web.cern.ch/press-releases/2009/06/cern-reports-progress-towards-lhc-restart |title=CERN reports on progress towards LHC restart |date=19 June 2009 |publisher=CERN Press Office |accessdate=21 July 2009
}}</ref>2009年11月20日，LHC重新注入粒子束。23日，LHC的兩道粒子束同時沿著圓形軌道循環，ATLAS探測器首先收集到質子質子碰撞數據，能量為450 GeV每粒子束。<ref name="Restart2009">{{cite web | url =http://cerncourier.com/cws/article/cern/41459 | title =THE LHC IS BACK: FOUR REMARKABLE WEEKS | last =Sutton | first =Christine | date =20 Jan 2010 | publisher =CERN COURIER}}</ref>之後，ATLAS探測器持續不斷的收集數據。在這期間，LHC能量也不停增加，到2009年底，已達1,180 GeV每粒子束，<ref name="Restart2009"/>整個2010年與2011年，能量為3,500 GeV每粒子束，2012年，又提升到4,000 GeV每粒子束。<ref>{{cite web | url =http://www.atlas.ch/news/2012/lhc-to-run-at-8tev.html | title =LHC 2012 Run at 8 TeV Has Started | date =19 Feb 2012 | website =ATLAS NEWS | publisher =ATLAS Experiment | deadurl =yes | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160305104012/http://www.atlas.ch/news/2012/lhc-to-run-at-8tev.html | archivedate =2016-03-05 }}</ref>之後關閉了兩年，在2015年，更提升到6,500 GeV每粒子束。<ref>{{cite web | url =http://atlas.ch/news/2015/atlas-completes-first-year-at-13-tev.html | title =ATLAS Completes First Year at 13 TeV | last =Anthony | first =Katarina | date =16 Dec 2015 | website =ATLAS NEWS | publisher =ATLAS Experiment | deadurl =yes | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160117090052/http://atlas.ch/news/2015/atlas-completes-first-year-at-13-tev.html | archivedate =2016-01-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url =http://www.atlas.ch/news/2015/atlas-begins-recording-physics-data-at-13-tev.html | title =ATLAS Begins Recording Physics Data at 13 TeV | date =3 Jun 2015 | website =ATLAS NEWS | publisher =ATLAS Experiment | deadurl =yes | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160305002833/http://www.atlas.ch/news/2015/atlas-begins-recording-physics-data-at-13-tev.html | archivedate =2016-03-05 }}</ref>

